      "id": "d6304d14932afa20",
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "text": "If your seminar aims at improving the skill of the participants, then a project serves well as an exam. A oral exam is also good, because you can get a feeling for how the participant solves problems. The disadvantage is that it is more work for you to find an appropriate mark. And the results are not as easy to prove and compare.\n  ",
      "id": "38dbbddbbb4216f6",
